{"tid":1835571,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"防疫症入侵  義大利查扣並銷毀9.5噸中国豬","createTime":"2020-01-23T01:45:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-23T01:55:29.000Z","uid":184679,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"48361207f57cc0ce50516c13cb9bb4a5275e44f2","tid":1835571,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T01:45:31.000Z","msg":"在中國爆發非洲豬瘟後，義大利衛生部已禁止中國豬肉進口，不過，義大利東北城市巴都亞警方1間中國公民經營倉庫裡，發現9.5噸中國豬肉，為防非洲豬瘟入侵，已將這批走私豬肉查扣並銷毀。<br />\n<br />\n路透報導，義大利東北城市巴都亞警方在巴都亞附近1間由中國公民經營的倉庫裡，這批非法豬肉被藏在自中國進口的蔬菜中。<br />\n<br />\n警方進一步指出，這批豬肉已被銷毀，至於該名男子則被控走私、從事有害食品交易以及散播動物疾病。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3048444\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3048444&d=EHipY5QqnFkcHnyd5ykVzG9Dn5prBKp8mj11ELPip4s%3D&h=7b9b277e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3048444&h=e876557e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3048444</a>"},{"pid":"9888d620d4da81efbea68455772f427418425112","tid":1835571,"uid":131188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T01:46:50.000Z","msg":"自己都唔夠食, 中國豬肉仲有得出口? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c0fd5900ad4c867aaaa61bb4e759c709696b4b8","tid":1835571,"uid":258649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T01:47:03.000Z","msg":"9.5噸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3688c6a5d8faf78daa57d839d200252970e67ee","tid":1835571,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9888d620d4da81efbea68455772f427418425112","tid":1835571,"uid":131188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T01:46:50.000Z"